#, no-c-format
msgid "Filename"
msgstr "Dateiname"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set a default filename for saved screenshots."
msgstr "Standardnamen für gespeicherte Bildschirmfotos einstellen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the following placeholders in the filename, which will be "
"replaced with actual text when the file is saved:"
